MARCSubfieldLabel: Number where instructions are found-single number or beginning number of span (R)
Justification for Mapping: The MARC 21 manual indicates that this field duplicates the classification number recorded in fields 082 and 083, so it does not need to be transformed. In any case, we are interested in the actual classification number that is assigned to the work, but we are not interested in how it is synthesized from simpler components.-Gordon 4/2/2024
